Subject: [CASE-{case_id}] Vulnerability Report — Validated as {severity}

Hello {researcher_name},

Thank you for submitting case {case_id}. We have completed our initial review of your report.

VALIDATION OUTCOME: Confirmed — {severity}

Our assessment:
- Vulnerability type: {vuln_type}
- Affected component: {component}
- Severity rationale: {severity_rationale}
  (including agentic impact factors: {agentic_factors})

REMEDIATION TIMELINE
Target fix date: {target_fix_date} ({sla_days} days from today per our {severity} SLA)
Next status update: {next_update_date}

COORDINATED DISCLOSURE
We will contact you before publishing any advisory to agree on a disclosure date and review your credit acknowledgement.

Please do not disclose this vulnerability publicly until we have coordinated a disclosure date.
Our safe harbour applies to your good-faith testing of in-scope systems as described in your report.

Kind regards,
{security_team_member}
Security Engineering, {organisation_name}
Case reference: {case_id}
